Changes in version 0.41.2
==============
- 14122018: Introduced fuzzy-matching of variable names in readces()
- 14122018: Removed warning for age-codes 3J, 5, 6 in readces()


Changes in version 0.41.1
==============
- 30122017: Added check for numeric dates and net lengths in readces() and updated help file
- 09042018: Made summary.ces() do something sensible when given a species summary object
- 15052018: Bugfix - readces() not reading alphabetic visits correctly
- 17052018: Bugfix - missed the visit column from missing.visits[] in extract.counts
- 14062018: Added ability for siteplot() to summarise catches per visit

Changes in version 0.41.0
==============
- 02102017: Altered model functions to cope with single sites 

